{"id":2158,"date":"2024-11-22T16:21:31","date_gmt":"2024-11-22T16:21:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=2158"},"modified":"2024-12-01T03:15:31","modified_gmt":"2024-12-01T03:15:31","slug":"happiness-checker","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/happiness-checker\/","title":{"rendered":"Happiness Checker (NPC)"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left widesecond\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td><strong>Dehara City<\/strong> &#8211; Inside of the house directly south of the Rift Cave entrance.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Purpose<\/th>\n<td>Checks the happiness of the first Pok\u00e9mon in the player\u2019s party.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Transaction Item<\/th>\n<td>N\/A<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Cost<\/th>\n<td>Free<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Dehara City Pok\u00e9mon Center and follow the path north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/01-pokemon-unbound-walking-north-from-the-dehara-city-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Walking north from the Dehara City Pokemon Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking north from the Dehara City Pokemon Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Walk past the first house to your east and enter the second one.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-house-south-of-rift-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the house south of Rift Cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the house south of Rift Cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Inside the house, interact with the closed doors to open them.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/03-pokemon-unbound-interacting-with-the-closed-doors.jpg\" alt=\"Interacting with the closed doors. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Interacting with the closed doors.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Happiness Checker is the blonde girl inside the room.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/04-pokemon-unbound-approaching-the-happiness-checker.jpg\" alt=\"Approaching the Happiness Checker. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Approaching the Happiness Checker.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Purpose<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/05-pokemon-unbound-the-happiness-checkers-service.jpg\" alt=\"The Happiness Checker\u2019s service. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Happiness Checker\u2019s service.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Happiness Checker can check and comments on the overall happiness\/friendship of the first Pokemon in your party.<\/p>\n<p>Alternatively, you can also go to the summary screen for any Pok\u00e9mon and look for the heart next to the Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s name. This will show their happiness level as well.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/06-pokemon-unbound-tapu-leles-summary-showing-his-overall-happiness.jpg\" alt=\"Tapu Lele\u2019s summary showing his overall happiness. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Tapu Lele\u2019s summary showing his overall happiness.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/misc-info\/useful-npcs\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"299\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/useful-npc-preview.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-conten